	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is this what you mean?
<br />
<br />20/70 -  NTSC/PAL VBlank Scanlines
<br />1 - Dummy Scanline (for pre-fetching tile and sprite data)
<br />240 - Render Scanlines
<br />1 - Dead Scanline (PPU does nothing at all)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


